  30 Jan 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> files/0.12-FLAGS.patch,
  +files/0.12-libnotify-0.7.patch, kerneloops-0.12-r1.ebuild:
  Fix building with x11-libs/libnotify >= 0.7. Fix missing -I and -l flags for
  dbus-glib-1 in -FLAGS.patch.

*kerneloops-0.12-r1 (07 Feb 2010)

  07 Feb 2010; Justin Lecher (jlec) <jlec@gentoo.org>
  +files/0.12-FLAGS.patch, kerneloops-0.12.ebuild,
  +kerneloops-0.12-r1.ebuild:
  Fix for bug 237940 & 238106
  Missing IUSE added

*kerneloops-0.12 (15 Sep 2008)

  15 Sep 2008; Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +kerneloops-0.12.ebuild:
  0.12 release. Removed -gtk option, too much of a pain to try to build
  without applet portion, so am giving up.

  07 Sep 2008; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> kerneloops-0.11.ebuild:
  add ~amd64, bug #236956

  28 Apr 2008; Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@gentoo.org>
